as, such as mergers, amalgamation, acquisition, valuation, etc. Further, it invests and trades in shares and securities; and invests in cash and derivative markets. The company was formerly known as Meenakshi Enterprises Limited and changed its name to JMJ Fintech Limited in June 2022. JMJ Fintech Limited was incorporated in 1982 and is based in Coimbatore, India."}}